import React from 'react'

import { IntroContainer, Heading, SubHeading } from './Intro.styles'

const Intro = () => {
    return (
        <IntroContainer>
            <Heading>
                Fabian Suffield
        </Heading>
            <SubHeading>
                web developer
        </SubHeading>
        </IntroContainer>
    )
}

export default Intro
